                <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/muirwd">Andrew</a>,
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cal1n/">Calin</a> and
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sallyhughes/">Sally</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 py-6 md:py-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2 lg:pb-8">Some of the folks giving their time</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
            {% for teamMember in data.team.records %}
                <li class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 flex p-2 md:p-3">
                    <div class="border border-blue-800 rounded-lg flex-grow bg-white flex flex-col mt-12">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center pt-6">
                            <div class="bg-cover bg-top pb-20 w-20 rounded-full shadow-2xl -mt-16" style="background-image: url('/images/team/{{ teamMember.fields["Name"] | slug }}.png')"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 flex flex-col flex-grow">
